title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Oh, Hello - I, CED
description:
Hear the St. Louis, MS born I, CED share how he embarks on his creative process to write his original music - from starting with the lyrics on certain tracks, to creating the music first on others. 
For more on Converse Rubber Tracks visit:
http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks
